  <deviceDescription>
                <description>
            <lang xml:lang="en">SSP 301 is a switch and repeater mains powered device,that forms part of a Z Wave Plus™ home automation network. that will switch a connected appliance either by the Z-Wave network or manually by pressing its integrated button.</lang>
          </description>
            <wakeupNote>
            <lang xml:lang="en"></lang>
          </wakeupNote>
            <inclusionNote>
            <lang xml:lang="en">Step 1: Unpack, and insert the
SSP 301 into the wall socket.
Ensure that the red-coloured
Network Status LED is flashing
(once per second).
Step-2: Z-Wave Plus™ commissioning
To include the SSP 301 onto a network, put the
controller into inclusion mode. Now, press and hold the
button on SSP 301 for 4 to 7 seconds then release.
The network status LED will start flashing (twice per
second) on successful start of
inclusion process.</lang>
          </inclusionNote>
            <productName>SSP 301</productName>
            <brandName>Secure </brandName>
            <productLine>SSP </productLine>
            <productCode>PMR000-Z23</productCode>
                        </deviceDescription>

